beer.beer_description:
Hazy Harvest is made with freshly picked Galaxy Hop cones from a nearby farm. Fresh Hop beers can only be made once a year using hops added to the brew on the day of their harvest.

This beer’s unique aromas are of peach and ripe melon. The finish has understated passionfruit and citrus notes synonymous with fresh Galaxy hops.
